spanGrp.span: `i retired from my service in the year 1954..'
Nga retired o ha u-snæm khatkhynde spah sanphaw soo
`In the year 1955, i went to Shillong.'
Ha u-snæm khatkhynde spah sanphaw san, lai shillong
`i went to Shillong by bus at 10:30 AM. just after passing Ummulong is a place called as Pynsum kule..'
hei-por chiphaw chitein da ka-bus lai shillong Hakhmat Ummulong, ha ka-thaw wa ong ki pyn-sum kule
`There is one old woman who died..'
`There was the generator that was kept in that bus, the generator fell over this woman and she died..'
Booh ki ka-generator, kylla ka-bus, ban ka-generator, yap ko, ka-wi
Nga yoh faint o, yaplær o
`There was also one man, the SDO of MeECL, whose hand was fractured in that incident..'
tæ u-wi u-tæ u-bru, u-SDO electric, khæñ ka-ni ka-kti
`My leg too got stuck on the roof of the bus.'
hei-tæ i-por, sah ka-ni ka-kjat o, ha ka-ni ka-tnoom yong ka-bus
`i tried to pull it out with force. after hearing that woman shouted Ah!! Mom, i am dying..'
dei-bor tdæh o ka. Katwa kiat ka-tæ ka-bru, Ah bei da yap o!!
`immediately i pulled out my leg and ran outside, there i saw this dead woman, the generator also was there..'
Tdæh o ka-ni ka-kjat, dæp nei-tæ tæ mih o cha lait tæ yoo o ya ka-ni ka-bru wa da yap, ka-generator læh æm
dæp nei-tæ nga liwan wot o cha yung
La ym kamtæ da yap o
